<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 via-white to-blue-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Esercizio 1: Sottolinea tutti gli indefiniti -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">1</span>
          <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm md:text-base font-bold whitespace-nowrap">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
        </div>
        <span>Sottolinea tutti gli <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold underline">indefiniti</span>.</span>
      </div>
    </h2>

    <!-- Hidden color selector -->
    <div class="hidden">
      <span data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-4 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed cursor-pointer">
      <p class="mb-3">Quando Emma si arrabbia prende <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">tutti</span> i colori che ha nel portapenne e inizia a disegnare. Non ne dimentica <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">nessuno</span>!</p>
      <p class="mb-3">Usa <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">molto</span> rosso, perché è arrabbiata; <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">parecchio</span> blu, perché è triste; <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">poco</span> nero, perché non le piace.</p>
      <p class="mb-3">Fa <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">tante</span> righe in <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">tutte</span> le direzioni: <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">alcune</span> sembrano gocce di pioggia, <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">altre</span> petardi che scoppiano… <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">certe</span> somigliano addirittura a delle lettere!</p>
      <p>Quando la rabbia passa, disegna <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">qualche</span> riga gialla: sono i raggi del sole che torna!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 2: Sottolinea aggettivi e cerchia pronomi indefiniti -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">2</span>
        <span>Sottolinea gli <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">aggettivi indefiniti<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-green-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span> e cerchia i <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">pronomi indefiniti<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>.</span>
      </div>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Ogni</span> volta che viene a trovarmi, la nonna mi porta <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">qualche</span> dolcetto.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Molti</span> bambini della mia classe sono figli unici, <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">alcuni</span> hanno un fratello o una sorella, <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">pochi</span> ne hanno più di uno.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Lucia ti ha chiesto <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">qualcosa</span> di me? Sono <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">parecchi</span> giorni che non la sento.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Non ho <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">altro</span> da aggiungere. Adesso potete farmi voi <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">qualche</span> domanda.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Chiunque</span> si affacciasse al finestrino non riusciva a vedere <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">niente</span>: c'era <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">troppa</span> nebbia.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 3: Completa con indefiniti -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">3</span>
        <span>Completa con gli <span class="text-green-600 font-bold underline">indefiniti</span> adatti, poi indica se hai scritto un <span class="underline">aggettivo</span> (A) o un <span class="underline">pronome</span> (P).</span>
      </div>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">•</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Alcuni|Molti|Pochi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">dei miei compagni possiedono un cane.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Puoi chiederlo a</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="chiunque|tutti" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">. Vedrai che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="nessuno" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">ti dirà che sono stato io.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Tutte" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">le sere la mamma beve una tisana prima di dormire.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Non mi hai dato</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="nessun|alcun" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">suggerimento.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Mancano</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="pochi|alcuni" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">giorni all'inizio delle vacanze.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Tutti" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">volevano parlare:</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="ognuno|ciascuno" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">aveva</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="qualcosa|molto" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">da dire.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Non ho fame: ho mangiato</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="molta|parecchia|troppa" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">pasta a pranzo.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Il problema era difficile ma</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="tutti" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700">i bambini sono riusciti a risolverlo.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
    Grammatica pp. <%= link_to "58", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p058"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "59", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p059"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise Controls -->
  <div class="mt-6">
    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'cyan', current_page: 'nvl5_gram_p159' %>
  </div>
</div>
